ination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >开发工具：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >window7,sts,Hbuilder,jdk7,oracle,tomcat,chrome</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=p  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >主要负责登录模块以及基础数据模块的功能实现,猪场老板和猪场员工分别对应不同的权限,猪场员工登陆后仅有数据录入功能,而老板登录后不仅可以录入数据;从宏观方面,还可以查看猪场实时动态数据,从微观方面,可以通过耳号精确查询每一只母猪的详细信息.</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=p  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目简介：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >该项目为猪场管理项目,致力于帮助猪场老板实时掌握猪场财政收入,生产动态,库存信息,以及根据录入的数据生成excel报表,动态图,帮助分析猪场潜在的威胁,警示猪场老板提前做好预防!</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=MsoNormal  style="word-break:break-all;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=600  valign=center  style="width:360.0000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><table class=MsoNormalTable  style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:5.4000pt;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=p  align=right  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:right;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:新宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2016/05&nbsp;-&nbsp;2016/12</span></b><b><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >速龙物流</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p></td></tr><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=p  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >1.参与基础信息管理模块；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2.编写服务器端的自定义分页工具类和业务接口；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >3编写DAO数据访问层；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >4.参与定区管理功能模块；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=p  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目简介：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >本项目是一个仓储物流管理系统，我们的系统和努力可以帮助生产事业、零售事业真正做到以最少的资金做最多的生意。该系统主要由四大模块组成，分别是订单业务模块、仓库业务模块、基础维护模块、系统维护模块。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=MsoNormal  style="word-break:break-all;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=600  valign=center  style="width:360.0000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><table class=MsoNormalTable  style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:5.4000pt;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=p  align=right  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:right;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:新宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2015/12&nbsp;-&nbsp;2016/03</span></b><b><span style="font-family:新宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >乐游酒店管理系统</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p></td></tr><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=p  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >后台管理员系统,客房类型设置、客房设置、操作员设置模块</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:13.2000pt;" ><td width=132  valign=center  style="width:79.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=424  valign=center  style="width:254.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 8.4000pt ;" ><p class=p  style="word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目简介：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >随着酒店业务的增加,为了提高酒店的管理水平，完成酒店业务规范化操作，提高酒店的管理效率，服务质量及酒店的入住率.酒店管理系统分为前台和后台:前台是酒店&nbsp;工作人员使用，包括入住登记、结账、预定、客户管理以及业务统计模块:后台是管理员管理系统使用，包括客房类型设置、客房设置、操作员设置模块&#160;&#160;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=MsoNormal  style="word-break:break-all;line-height:12.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:7.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><